@gatewayBaseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### API Gateway Tests

### 1. Gateway Health Route (Auth Service via Gateway)
# Check if the API Gateway is routing to Auth Service successfully.
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/auth/test

###

### 2. User Signup via Gateway
# Register a new user through API Gateway.
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@fincz.com",
    "password": "java@123"
}

###

### 3. User Login via Gateway
# Authenticate through API Gateway and store the JWT.
# @name login
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@fincz.com",
    "password": "java@123"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 3.1 Create User Profile via Gateway
# Create a profile using the User Service through API Gateway.
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@fincz.com",
    "password": "dummy_password"
}

###

### User Service via Gateway

### 4. Get Current User (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Update Current User (Gateway)
PUT {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Updated User",
    "phone": "+12345678901",
    "age": 30,
    "occupation": "Engineer",
    "financialGoals": "Save for retirement"
}

###

### 6. Get User by ID (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Portfolio Service via Gateway

### 7. Add Investment (Gateway)
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "stock",
    "name": "Tata Consultancy Services",
    "symbol": "TCS.NS",
    "units": 10,
    "buyPrice": 3200.50
}

###

### 8. Get Portfolio (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Get Net Worth (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio/networth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. Add Mutual Fund Investment (Gateway)
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "mf",
    "name": "HDFC Flexi Cap Fund",
    "symbol": "HDFCFCF",
    "units": 100,
    "buyPrice": 150.75
}

###

### 11. Get Stock Portfolio (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio/type/stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Market Data Service via Gateway

### 12. Get Stock Price (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/market/price/TCS.NS

###

### 13. Get Mutual Fund Price (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/market/price/HDFCFCF

###

### Notification Service via Gateway

### 14. Notification Service Health Check (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/notifications/test

###

### 15. Send Notification (Gateway)
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "toEmail": "test@fincz.com",
  "subject": "Portfolio Update",
  "message": "Your portfolio has been updated successfully!"
}

###

### 16. Get User Notifications (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 17. Trigger Tax Reminder (Gateway)
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/notifications/tax-reminder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 18. Trigger Portfolio Alert (Gateway)
POST {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/notifications/portfolio-alert
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Additional Portfolio Tests via Gateway

### 19. Get Mutual Fund Portfolio (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/portfolio/type/mf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Additional Market Data Tests via Gateway

### 20. Get Stock Price for Different Symbol (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/market/price/INFY.NS

###

### 21. Get Mutual Fund Price for Different Fund (Gateway)
GET {{gatewayBaseUrl}}/market/price/SBIBCF
